race.comment: FLYING SEAL (1) was in the money last time at this track (16.58) in a Grade 5, finishing a one length second. Unbeaten in two runs from this draw. Rates on top and should go close. SWIFT RACER (8) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 4 lengths at this track in a handy 16.70. Wide box to overcome but goes well over this trip. One of main contenders. DAYTONA BEACH (3) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with two wins and a placing from four tries. Placed last time (16.62) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing second and beaten 3.5 lengths. Looks suited here and can measure up. PUSHING LIMITS (6) looks an each-way chance.
